42  public static class Sdl
43  {
47  static Sdl()
48  {
49  if (RuntimeInformation.IsOSPlatform(OSPlatform.OSX))
50  {
51  switch (RuntimeInformation.ProcessArchitecture)
52  {
53  case Architecture.Arm64:
54  EmbeddedDllClass.ExtractEmbeddedDlls("sdl2.dylib", NativeGraphic.osx_arm64_sdl2);
55  break;
56  case Architecture.X64:
57  EmbeddedDllClass.ExtractEmbeddedDlls("sdl2.dylib", NativeGraphic.osx_x64_sdl2);
58  break;
59  }
60  }
61 
62  if (RuntimeInformation.IsOSPlatform(OSPlatform.Windows))
63  {
64  switch (RuntimeInformation.ProcessArchitecture)
65  {
66  case Architecture.Arm64:
67  EmbeddedDllClass.ExtractEmbeddedDlls("sdl2.dll", NativeGraphic.win_arm64_sdl2);
68  break;
69  case Architecture.X86:
70  EmbeddedDllClass.ExtractEmbeddedDlls("sdl2.dll", NativeGraphic.win_x86_sdl2);
71  break;
72  case Architecture.X64:
73  EmbeddedDllClass.ExtractEmbeddedDlls("sdl2.dll", NativeGraphic.win_x64_sdl2);
74  break;
75  }
76  }
77 
78  if (RuntimeInformation.IsOSPlatform(OSPlatform.Linux))
79  {
80  switch (RuntimeInformation.ProcessArchitecture)
81  {
82  case Architecture.Arm64:
83  EmbeddedDllClass.ExtractEmbeddedDlls("sdl2.so", NativeGraphic.linux_arm64_sdl2);
84  break;
85  case Architecture.X64:
86  EmbeddedDllClass.ExtractEmbeddedDlls("sdl2.so", NativeGraphic.linux_x64_sdl2);
87  break;
88  }
89  }
90  }

95  private const string NativeLibName = "sdl2";

98 
104  internal static int Utf8Size(string str)
105  {
106  if (str == null)
107  {
108  return 0;
109  }
110 
111  return str.Length * 4 + 1;
112  }
113 
121  internal static unsafe byte* Utf8Encode(string str, byte* buffer, int bufferSize)
122  {
123  if (str == null)
124  {
125  return (byte*) 0;
126  }
127 
128  fixed (char* strPtr = str)
129  {
130  Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(strPtr, str.Length + 1, buffer, bufferSize);
131  }
132 
133  return buffer;
134  }
135 
136 
142  internal static unsafe byte* Utf8EncodeHeap(string str)
143  {
144  if (str == null)
145  {
146  return (byte*) 0;
147  }
148 
149  int bufferSize = Utf8Size(str);
150  byte* buffer = (byte*) Marshal.AllocHGlobal(bufferSize);
151  fixed (char* strPtr = str)
152  {
153  Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(strPtr, str.Length + 1, buffer, bufferSize);
154  }
155 
156  return buffer;
157  }
158 
159 
166  public static unsafe string UTF8_ToManaged(IntPtr s, bool freePtr = false)
167  {
168  if (s == IntPtr.Zero)
169  {
170  return null;
171  }
172 
173 
174  byte* ptr = (byte*) s;
175  while (*ptr != 0)
176  {
177  ptr++;
178  }
179  int len = (int) (ptr - (byte*) s);
180  if (len == 0)
181  {
182  return string.Empty;
183  }
184 
185  char* chars = stackalloc char[len];
186  int strLen = Encoding.UTF8.GetChars((byte*) s, len, chars, len);
187  string result = new string(chars, 0, strLen);
188 
189 
190  if (freePtr)
191  {
192  SDL_free(s);
193  }
194 
195  return result;
196  }
197 
198 
207  public static uint SDL_FOURCC(byte a, byte b, byte c, byte d) => (uint) (a | (b << 8) | (c << 16) | (d << 24));

335  [DllImport(NativeLibName, EntryPoint = "SDL_RWFromFile", CallingConvention = CallingConvention.Cdecl)]
336  private static extern unsafe IntPtr INTERNAL_SDL_RWFromFile(
337  byte* file,
338  byte* mode
339  );
340 
347  public static unsafe IntPtr SDL_RWFromFile(
348  string file,
349  string mode
350  )
351  {
352  byte* utf8File = Utf8EncodeHeap(file);
353  byte* utf8Mode = Utf8EncodeHeap(mode);
354  IntPtr rwOps = INTERNAL_SDL_RWFromFile(
355  utf8File,
356  utf8Mode
357  );
358  Marshal.FreeHGlobal((IntPtr) utf8Mode);
359  Marshal.FreeHGlobal((IntPtr) utf8File);
360  return rwOps;
361  }

610  [DllImport(NativeLibName, EntryPoint = "SDL_LoadFile", CallingConvention = CallingConvention.Cdecl)]
611  private static extern unsafe IntPtr INTERNAL_SDL_LoadFile(byte* file, out IntPtr datasize);
612 
619  public static unsafe IntPtr SDL_LoadFile(string file, out IntPtr datasize)
620  {
621  byte* utf8File = Utf8EncodeHeap(file);
622  IntPtr result = INTERNAL_SDL_LoadFile(utf8File, out datasize);
623  Marshal.FreeHGlobal((IntPtr) utf8File);
624  return result;
625  }

2065  [DllImport(NativeLibName, EntryPoint = "SDL_ShowMessageBox", CallingConvention = CallingConvention.Cdecl)]
2066  private static extern int INTERNAL_SDL_ShowMessageBox([In] ref InternalSdlMessageBoxData messageboxdata, out int buttonid);
2067 
2068 
2074  private static IntPtr INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(string str)
2075  {
2076  if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(str))
2077  {
2078  return IntPtr.Zero;
2079  }
2080 
2081  byte[] bytes = Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(str + '\0');
2082  IntPtr mem = SDL_malloc((IntPtr) bytes.Length);
2083  Marshal.Copy(bytes, 0, mem, bytes.Length);
2084  return mem;
2085  }
2086 
2093  public static unsafe int SDL_ShowMessageBox([In] ref SdlMessageBoxData messageboxdata, out int buttonid)
2094  {
2095  InternalSdlMessageBoxData data = new InternalSdlMessageBoxData
2096  {
2097  flags = messageboxdata.flags,
2098  window = messageboxdata.window,
2099  title = INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(messageboxdata.title),
2100  message = INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(messageboxdata.message),
2101  numbuttons = messageboxdata.numbuttons
2102  };
2103 
2104  InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData[] buttons = new InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData[messageboxdata.numbuttons];
2105  for (int i = 0; i < messageboxdata.numbuttons; i++)
2106  {
2107  buttons[i] = new InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData
2108  {
2109  flags = messageboxdata.buttons[i].flags,
2110  buttonid = messageboxdata.buttons[i].buttonid,
2111  text = INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(messageboxdata.buttons[i].text)
2112  };
2113  }
2114 
2115  if (messageboxdata.colorScheme != null)
2116  {
2117  data.colorScheme = Marshal.AllocHGlobal(Marshal.SizeOf(typeof(SdlMessageBoxColorScheme)));
2118  Marshal.StructureToPtr(messageboxdata.colorScheme.Value, data.colorScheme, false);
2119  }
2120 
2121  int result;
2122  fixed (InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData* buttonsPtr = &buttons[0])
2123  {
2124  data.buttons = (IntPtr) buttonsPtr;
2125  result = INTERNAL_SDL_ShowMessageBox(ref data, out buttonid);
2126  }
2127 
2128  Marshal.FreeHGlobal(data.colorScheme);
2129  for (int i = 0; i < messageboxdata.numbuttons; i++)
2130  {
2131  SDL_free(buttons[i].text);
2132  }
2133 
2134  SDL_free(data.message);
2135  SDL_free(data.title);
2136 
2137  return result;
2138  }

6070  public static uint SDL_DEFINE_PIXELFOURCC(byte a, byte b, byte c, byte d) => SDL_FOURCC(a, b, c, d);
6071 
6081  public static uint SDL_DEFINE_PIXELFORMAT(
6082  SdlPixelType type,
6083  uint order,
6084  SdlPackedLayout layout,
6085  byte bits,
6086  byte bytes
6087  )
6088  => (uint) (
6089  (1 << 28) |
6090  ((byte) type << 24) |
6091  ((byte) order << 20) |
6092  ((byte) layout << 16) |
6093  (bits << 8) |
6094  bytes
6095  );
6096 
6102  public static byte SDL_PIXELFLAG(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 28) & 0x0F);
6103 
6109  public static byte SDL_PIXELTYPE(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 24) & 0x0F);
6110 
6116  public static byte SDL_PIXELORDER(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 20) & 0x0F);
6117 
6123  public static byte SDL_PIXELLAYOUT(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 16) & 0x0F);
6124 
6130  public static byte SDL_BITSPERPIXEL(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 8) & 0xFF);
6131 
6137  public static byte SDL_BYTESPERPIXEL(uint x)
6138  {
6139  if (SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_FOURCC(x))
6140  {
6141  if (x == SdlPixelformatYuy2 ||
6142  x == SdlPixelformatUyvy ||
6143  x == SdlPixelformatYvyu)
6144  {
6145  return 2;
6146  }
6147 
6148  return 1;
6149  }
6150 
6151  return (byte) (x & 0xFF);
6152  }
6153 
6159  public static bool SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_INDEXED(uint format)
6160  {
6161  if (SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_FOURCC(format))
6162  {
6163  return false;
6164  }
6165 
6166  SdlPixelType pType =
6167  (SdlPixelType) SDL_PIXELTYPE(format);
6168  return pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeIndex1 ||
6169  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeIndex4 ||
6170  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeIndex8;
6171  }
6172 
6178  public static bool SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_PACKED(uint format)
6179  {
6180  if (SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_FOURCC(format))
6181  {
6182  return false;
6183  }
6184 
6185  SdlPixelType pType =
6186  (SdlPixelType) SDL_PIXELTYPE(format);
6187  return pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypePacked8 ||
6188  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypePacked16 ||
6189  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypePacked32;
6190  }
6191 
6197  public static bool SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_ARRAY(uint format)
6198  {
6199  if (SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_FOURCC(format))
6200  {
6201  return false;
6202  }
6203 
6204  SdlPixelType pType =
6205  (SdlPixelType) SDL_PIXELTYPE(format);
6206  return pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayu8 ||
6207  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayu16 ||
6208  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayu32 ||
6209  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayf16 ||
6210  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayf32;
6211  }
6212 
6218  public static bool SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_ALPHA(uint format)
6219  {
6220  if (SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_PACKED(format))
6221  {
6222  SdlPackedOrder pOrder =
6223  (SdlPackedOrder) SDL_PIXELORDER(format);
6224  return pOrder == SdlPackedOrder.SdlPackedorderArgb ||
6225  pOrder == SdlPackedOrder.SdlPackedorderRgba ||
6226  pOrder == SdlPackedOrder.SdlPackedorderAbgr ||
6227  pOrder == SdlPackedOrder.SdlPackedorderBgra;
6228  }
6229 
6230  if (SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_ARRAY(format))
6231  {
6232  SdlArrayOrder aOrder =
6233  (SdlArrayOrder) SDL_PIXELORDER(format);
6234  return aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderArgb ||
6235  aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderRgba ||
6236  aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderAbgr ||
6237  aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderBgra;
6238  }
6239 
6240  return false;
6241  }

6248  public static bool SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_FOURCC(uint format) => (format == 0) && (SDL_PIXELFLAG(format) != 1);

8023  [DllImport(NativeLibName, CallingConvention = CallingConvention.Cdecl)]

8025  out IntPtr filter,
8026  out IntPtr userdata
8027  );
8028 
8035  public static SdlBool SDL_GetEventFilter(
8036  out SdlEventFilter filter,
8037  out IntPtr userdata
8038  )
8039  {
8040  IntPtr result = IntPtr.Zero;
8041  SdlBool retval = SDL_GetEventFilter(out result, out userdata);
8042  if (result != IntPtr.Zero)
8043  {
8044  filter = (SdlEventFilter) Marshal.GetDelegateForFunctionPointer(
8045  result,
8046  typeof(SdlEventFilter)
8047  );
8048  }
8049  else
8050  {
8051  filter = null;
8052  }
8053 
8054  return retval;
8055  }

9639  IntPtr gamecontroller,
9640  SdlGameControllerAxis axis
9641  );

9649  public static SdlGameControllerButtonBind SDL_GameControllerGetBindForAxis(
9650  IntPtr gamecontroller,
9651  SdlGameControllerAxis axis
9652  )
9653  {
9654  // This is guaranteed to never be null
9655  InternalSdlGameControllerButtonBind dumb = INTERNAL_SDL_GameControllerGetBindForAxis(
9656  gamecontroller,
9657  axis
9658  );
9659  SdlGameControllerButtonBind result = new SdlGameControllerButtonBind();
9660  result.bindType = (SdlGameControllerBindType) dumb.bindType;
9661  result.value.hat.hat = dumb.unionVal0;
9662  result.value.hat.hat_mask = dumb.unionVal1;
9663  return result;
9664  }
